<paragraph blockId="13.[168,776,1613,2091]" pageId="13" pageNumber="1016">
Cryptophyte, endemic to mountain ranges of 
<collectingRegion country="Argentina" name="Buenos Aires" pageId="13" pageNumber="1016">Buenos Aires province</collectingRegion>
. Vulnerable due to restricted habitat (
<bibRefCitation author="Delucchi G" box="[175,338,1862,1886]" pageId="13" pageNumber="1016" pagination="19 - 31" refId="ref30263" refString="Delucchi G (2006) Las especies vegetales amenazadas de la Provincia de Buenos Aires: una actualizacion. Aprona Boletin Cientifico 39: 19 - 31." type="journal article" year="2006">Delucchi 2006</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
